=Episode 14=
(I Share Every Trait She Has)

2
00:00:10,180 --> 00:00:10,980
So, Ye Zhongjue

3
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:12,580
does have a female best friend
in the company.

4
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,660
A true rich beauty.

5
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:19,060
She is even Jueshi Group's vice CEO.

6
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,940
They seem perfect for each other.

7
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:24,340
Listen,

8
00:00:24,580 --> 00:00:26,500
when it comes to things like this,
you mustn't get into a fight with her.

9
00:00:26,660 --> 00:00:28,460
Do not argue with her
in front of Ye Zhongjue.

10
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:29,660
You need to show affection.

11
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:30,580
As much as you can.

12
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:33,220
Show Jian Jie that you
have a strong bond with him.

13
00:00:33,220 --> 00:00:34,020
No one can do you apart.

14
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:37,940
Jian Jie is not to be underestimated.

15
00:00:38,660 --> 00:00:39,820
The closer she is to him,

16
00:00:40,180 --> 00:00:42,060
the more she may become my obstacle.

17
00:00:43,180 --> 00:00:43,780
That's right.

18
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:45,420
Or you might end up gaining nothing

19
00:00:45,660 --> 00:00:46,820
and losing everything.

20
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:48,860
You are right.

21
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:50,580
I must make sure she disappears.

22
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:52,740
That's the right attitude.

23
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:54,220
Here, cheers.

24
00:01:00,420 --> 00:01:01,470
=Trick in Love=

25
00:01:01,470 --> 00:01:02,980
(Adapted from the novel
"Mr. Intrigue's Love Game" by Yun Qi Mo Li)

26
00:01:02,980 --> 00:01:04,660
Mr. CEO! Help!

27
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:06,340
