63
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:36,340
Of course I want to spend it with you!

64
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:40,740
But you made me angry.

65
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:42,540
Don't be angry.

66
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,140
Let's not talk about
those upsetting things.

67
00:02:44,180 --> 00:02:45,460
You made me angry.

68
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,540
It's all my fault.

69
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,740
(You like him,)

70
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:59,340
(but you're afraid to tell him?)

71
00:03:00,780 --> 00:03:03,780
(Because you are scared of rejection.)

72
00:03:06,825 --> 00:03:10,675
(Ye Zhongjue)
(Can you come out...)

73
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:22,660
Stay here for just a little while.

74
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:23,860
I'll go get you your clothes.

75
00:03:25,140 --> 00:03:25,820
Okay.

76
